data.description: Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom all-brick home in the heart of Sherwood! Situated just minutes away from shopping, dining, and various recreational activities, this residence offers both convenience and comfort. As you step inside, you're greeted by the warm embrace of home. This inviting residence boasts three cozy bedrooms, providing ample space for relaxation and entertaining. The master bedroom features an en-suite half bath, offering a touch of privacy and convenience. Outside, this property truly shines. Sitting on a spacious corner lot spanning .43 acres, the home offers a large front and backyard, perfect for outdoor activities and gatherings. Additionally, a 16'x30' shop with a garage provides ample storage space for tools, equipment, or hobbies. Don't miss your chance to own this wonderful home in Sherwood, offering a perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and charm.
